Date: Tue, 17 May 2022 13:18:29 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] odl: tr181-firewall.odl: enable support for defaults.d
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

So the firewall functionality can be extended from external packages.

Signed-off-by: Petr Å tetiar <ynezz@true.cz>
---
 odl/tr181-firewall.odl | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/odl/tr181-firewall.odl b/odl/tr181-firewall.odl
index 060891d84e91..3be0efe1f507 100644
--- a/odl/tr181-firewall.odl
+++ b/odl/tr181-firewall.odl
@@ -92,6 +92,8 @@
 
     odl = {
         dm-save = true,
+        dm-load = true,
+        dm-defaults = "defaults.d/",
         dm-save-on-changed = true,
         dm-save-delay = 1000,
         directory = "${storage-path}/odl"
